{"word":"συγκαλέω","slug":"συγκαλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συγϰαλέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καλέω\">καλέω</a></el>; ‘call together’] ‘announce to gather as a group’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b>summon <a href='B:480 15:16'>Mk 15:16</a>; <a href='B:490 15:6'>Lk 15:6</a>, <a href='B:490 15:9'>9</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on official business <b><a href='B:510 5:21'>Ac 5:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>call to one’s side, summon <a href='B:490 9:1'>Lk 9:1</a>; <a href='B:490 23:13'>23:13</a>; <a href='B:510 10:24'>Ac 10:24</a>; <a href='B:510 28:17'>28:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συγκακουχέομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συγκαλύπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}